{
  "chapter": 56,
  "chapter_summary": "耿秀凤告知江海天其亲侄儿叶慕华的真实身份。叶慕华在森林中拦截叶凌风，双方展开激战。叶凌风逃向叶屠户残军求救，宇文雄、江晓芙、钟秀先后拦截。萧志远率义军杀出，叶屠户兵败被擒。叶凌风抢马逃窜，遇归古愚官军正被竺尚父义军围攻，归古愚被耿秀凤部击杀。尉迟炯、祈圣因夫妇拦截叶凌风，谷中莲从马萨儿国探亲归来，误认叶凌风为亲侄儿出手相救。江海天赶到，用石子击落谷中莲暗器，揭露真相。叶慕华正式拜江海天为师，江晓芙与宇文雄婚事确定，众人北上助张教主起义。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_hai_tian",
      "speaker_name": "江海天",
      "listener": "char_geng_xiu_feng",
      "text": "我的亲侄儿，他是谁。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_geng_xiu_feng",
      "speaker_name": "耿秀凤",
      "listener": "char_jiang_hai_tian",
      "text": "他是叶冲霄之子，从前有个名字叫叶凌风，但给叶屠户的儿子冒用了这个名字之后，他现在就只用叶慕华这个名字了。你的徒弟宇文雄和他一同入川，他现在是援川义军的统领。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_hai_tian",
      "speaker_name": "江海天",
      "listener": "char_geng_xiu_feng",
      "text": "好，那你就带我去见他吧。可这是你帮我的忙，不是我帮你的忙啊。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_geng_xiu_feng",
      "speaker_name": "耿秀凤",
      "listener": "char_jiang_hai_tian",
      "text": "不，不，是你帮我的忙，也是帮你侄儿的忙。叶慕华刚才发现林子里有一个人，可能就是冒充他身份的那个叶凌风，他已经往东边追下去了！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "叶凌风",
      "listener": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "text": "又是你！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "叶慕华",
      "listener": "char_ye_ling_feng",
      "text": "是呀，这可真是太不巧了吧，咱们又陌路相逢了。你两次害我不死，又两次在我手下侥幸逃生。今日相逢，除非是你有本领第三次害死了我，否则你要想逃走只怕就不那么容易了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "叶凌风",
      "listener": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "text": "不错，我是曾经害过你两次，但我也曾经救过你一次啊！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "叶慕华",
      "listener": "char_ye_ling_feng",
      "text": "你不提也还罢了，你第一次救我，其实就是为了害我。你冒用了我的身份，骗了江大侠，害了多少人，造了多少孽！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "叶凌风",
      "listener": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "text": "好，你既不谅，那就只好拚个你死我活了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "叶慕华",
      "listener": "char_ye_ling_feng",
      "text": "好贼子，死到临头，还敢偷施暗算。来而不往非礼也，看剑！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "叶凌风",
      "listener": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "text": "谁死谁活，那也难说得很多。哼，且叫你知道我的剑法的厉害！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "叶慕华",
      "listener": "char_ye_ling_feng",
      "text": "好小子，今日不是你死，便是我亡！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "叶凌风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "爹爹，我在这儿，快来救我！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "叶慕华",
      "listener": "char_ye_ling_feng",
      "text": "想要逃么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_tu_hu",
      "speaker_name": "叶屠户",
      "listener": "char_ye_ling_feng",
      "text": "宗儿，快来！呀，老天保佑，想不到咱们父子还能相见！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wen_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "宇文雄",
      "listener": "char_ye_ling_feng",
      "text": "贼子往哪里逃？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "叶凌风",
      "listener": "char_yu_wen_xiong",
      "text": "你眼中没有师兄，你的本领却还未必胜得过我！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "叶凌风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "下去！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "叶凌风",
      "listener": "char_zhong_xiu",
      "text": "秀妹，我纵有千般不是，也请你念在往日之情！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "叶凌风",
      "listener": "char_zhong_xiu",
      "text": "来得好，你既不念旧情，可也休怪我下得辣手了！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "叶凌风",
      "listener": "char_zhong_xiu",
      "text": "滚下来！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_zhi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "萧志远",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "天网恢恢，疏而不漏！好呀，今日叫你们父子俩一路走吧！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "叶慕华",
      "listener": "char_xiao_zhi_yuan",
      "text": "萧大哥，让我！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_zhi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "萧志远",
      "listener": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "text": "好，你吃小的，我吃老的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_tu_hu",
      "speaker_name": "叶屠户",
      "listener": "char_ye_ling_feng",
      "text": "想不到我手握兵符，独当一面，今日却落到如斯田地。宗儿，你自己逃生去吧！",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_zhi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "萧志远",
      "listener": "char_ye_tu_hu",
      "text": "叶屠户，你平生杀人也杀得够了，鲜血染红了你的顶子，如今该轮到我们来取你的项上人头啦！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_tu_hu",
      "speaker_name": "叶屠户",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我是朝廷命官，死也不能死在贼寇之手。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_tu_hu",
      "speaker_name": "叶屠户",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "士可杀而不可辱，士可杀而不可辱。你干脆就把我一刀杀了吧。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_zhi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "萧志远",
      "listener": "char_ye_tu_hu",
      "text": "你不过是鞑子皇帝的一条走狗，狗嘴里不长象牙，亏你还敢说什么气节？莫玷辱了一个士字！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_zhi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "萧志远",
      "listener": "char_ye_tu_hu",
      "text": "你们的朝廷有你们的王法，我们也有我们的民法。小金川的老百姓吃尽你的苦头，死在你的屠刀之下也不知多少，你想这么便宜就私自了结么？告诉你，我们要把你押回小金川去，让老百姓都来看你受我们的明正典刑。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_geng_xiu_feng",
      "speaker_name": "耿秀凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们去告诉归德堡的乡亲，咱们只是严惩首恶，胁从不究。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_gu_yu",
      "speaker_name": "归古愚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "反了，反了！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_geng_xiu_feng",
      "speaker_name": "耿秀凤",
      "listener": "char_gui_gu_yu",
      "text": "当然是反了！归老贼，你作威作福的日子已经完结啦！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_geng_xiu_feng",
      "speaker_name": "耿秀凤",
      "listener": "char_yu_wen_xiong",
      "text": "咱们可以上去看看，看叶大哥是否已把那好贼除了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wen_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "宇文雄",
      "listener": "char_geng_xiu_feng",
      "text": "不错，咱们去看这好贼如何下场吧。就只怕看不到了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "叶慕华",
      "listener": "char_ye_ling_feng",
      "text": "起来，再打！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "叶慕华",
      "listener": "char_jiang_hai_tian",
      "text": "都是侄儿做错了事，爹娘命我投亲，我却一直没有来拜谒姑父、姑母。又误信了这个奸贼，以致给他冒充了我的身份，生出了这许多祸患。",
      "tone": "愧疚",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_hai_tian",
      "speaker_name": "江海天",
      "listener": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "text": "我也有失察之处，好在终于水落石出，你也替我清理了门户了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_hai_tian",
      "speaker_name": "江海天",
      "listener": "char_gu_zhong_lian",
      "text": "你失了一个假的侄儿，得回一个真的侄儿。这可该大大高兴了吧！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_zhong_lian",
      "speaker_name": "谷中莲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁敢伤我徒儿？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_zhong_lian",
      "speaker_name": "谷中莲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有我在此，谁敢伤你？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_zhong_lian",
      "speaker_name": "谷中莲",
      "listener": "char_jiang_hai_tian",
      "text": "你说谁是我的亲侄儿？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_hai_tian",
      "speaker_name": "江海天",
      "listener": "char_gu_zhong_lian",
      "text": "怪不得你不明白，我也是刚才才知道的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_hai_tian",
      "speaker_name": "江海天",
      "listener": "char_gu_zhong_lian",
      "text": "他才是你的亲侄儿，那奸细是冒充的。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_zhong_lian",
      "speaker_name": "谷中莲",
      "listener": "char_jiang_hai_tian",
      "text": "你，你说什么？叶凌风当真是奸细又是冒充我的侄儿的吗？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_hai_tian",
      "speaker_name": "江海天",
      "listener": "char_gu_zhong_lian",
      "text": "不错，他是叶屠户的儿子，咱们夫妻都受他蒙骗了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_zhong_lian",
      "speaker_name": "谷中莲",
      "listener": "char_jiang_hai_tian",
      "text": "这，这是怎么一回事？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_hai_tian",
      "speaker_name": "江海天",
      "listener": "char_gu_zhong_lian",
      "text": "你就快明白了，你瞧他们都来了。我慢慢说给你听，另外一些细节，他们也会告诉你的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_sheng_yin",
      "speaker_name": "祈圣因",
      "listener": "char_gu_zhong_lian",
      "text": "谷女侠，你错了，快住手！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "江晓芙",
      "listener": "char_gu_zhong_lian",
      "text": "妈，我一直说雄哥是好人，这厮才是奸细，你不相信，现在你的真假侄儿都在这儿，你相信了吧？爹，你告诉了妈妈没有？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_hai_tian",
      "speaker_name": "江海天",
      "listener": "char_jiang_xiao_fu",
      "text": "这好贼极工心计，连我都受他的蒙骗，你怎能单怪你妈？嗯，我正等着你来才好告诉你妈呢。我说一半，你说一半。对啦，还有尉迟舵主和祈女侠也是受了这奸细的谋害的，咱们把所知道的说出来，你妈就明白了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_geng_xiu_feng",
      "speaker_name": "耿秀凤",
      "listener": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "text": "华哥，祝你手刃仇人，我也要报仇去了！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_zhong_lian",
      "speaker_name": "谷中莲",
      "listener": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "text": "当初这奸贼拿你爹爹的信来见我，我本来有点疑心的，却给他骗过了。好侄儿，你何不早说，我刚才几乎误伤了你。可是，你还不仅是应该叫我做姑母呢，你姑父是叫你替他清理门户的，你懂不懂？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "叶慕华",
      "listener": "char_jiang_hai_tian",
      "text": "多谢姑父肯将我收列门墙。",
      "tone": "感激",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_zhong_lian",
      "speaker_name": "谷中莲",
      "listener": "char_yu_wen_xiong",
      "text": "当初我错怪了你，令你受了许多冤屈。",
      "tone": "愧疚",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wen_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "宇文雄",
      "listener": "char_gu_zhong_lian",
      "text": "当初谁也不知道这奸贼如此阴毒，师母执行门规，是应该的。徒儿怎敢有丝毫埋怨。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_hai_tian",
      "speaker_name": "江海天",
      "listener": "char_yu_wen_xiong",
      "text": "你把我的话告诉了芙儿没有？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wen_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "宇文雄",
      "listener": "char_jiang_hai_tian",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "江晓芙",
      "listener": "char_yu_wen_xiong",
      "text": "师哥，我爹爹叫你告诉我什么？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_hai_tian",
      "speaker_name": "江海天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "叫他一生照顾你。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_hai_tian",
      "speaker_name": "江海天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不过你们年纪都小，过两年再办喜事也还不迟。如今小金川之围是解了，但鞑子还占着咱们汉人的江山，多少地方的老百姓还在受着苦难。我准备北上去助张教主再次起义，你们随我去吧。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 56
    }
  ],
